{\li0 \f2 \qj \b0 \ri0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
{\li0 \f2 \qj \b0 \ri0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
{\f2 \strike0 \ul0 \b0 \sa0 \sb0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
Petitioner, Theon Jackson, is a mentally defective deaf mute with a mental level of a pre-school child. He cannot read, write, or otherwise communicate except through limited sign language. In May 1968, at age 27, he was charged 
}
