On this evidence, the trial court found that Jackson \u8216\'3flack(ed) comprehension sufficient to make his defense,\u8217\'3f s 9\u8212\'3f1706a, and ordered him committed to the Indiana Department of Mental Health until such time as that Department should certify to the court that \u8216\'3fthe defendant is sane.\u8217\'3f
\par 
}
}
}
{\li0 \f2 \qj \b0 \ri0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
