Petitioner\rquote s counsel then filed a motion for a new trial, contending that there was no evidence that Jackson was \u8216\'3finsane,\u8217\'3f or that he would ever attain a status which the court might regard as 
}
{\f2 \b1 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_708_1849_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_708_1849_1}
