{\f2 \strike0 \ul0 \b0 \sa0 \sb0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
 For instance, s 4.06(3) of the Model Penal Code would permit an incompetent accused\rquote s attorney to contest any issue \u8216\'3fsusceptible of fair determination prior to trial and without the personal participation of the defendant.\u8217\'3f An alternative draft of s 4.06(4) of the Model Penal Code would also permit an evidentiary hearing at which certain 
}
{\f2 \b1 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_pp_sp_780_741_1}{\*\bkmkend co_pp_sp_780_741_1}
