{\f2 \strike0 \ul0 \b0 \sa0 \sb0 \fs20 \cf1 \i0 
 We do not read this Court\rquote s previous decisions
}
{\f2 \b0 \fs16 \cf1 \i0 
{\*\bkmkstart co_footnoteReference_B032311972127136_ID}{\*\bkmkend co_footnoteReference_B032311972127136_ID}
